usage_frame: >
  YAWN is a mirror. Use it by filling out .yawn files like madlibs for your
  life, projects, records, and next moves. Any AI can help you mirror and
  organize, but the human remains the source of authorization.

folder_node_rule: >
  Every folder is a knowledge node and mental-model node. Each folder should
  contain node.yawn as its local orientation card.

